the ghost and mrs. muir is a 1947 american comedy film directed by joseph l. mankiewicz and starring peter pan , miss sloane and mary muir . the film is based on the novel of the same name by josephine leslie . the film is a remake of the 1947 film the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) .